1
00:00:01,401 --> 00:00:02,502
And that's a wrap!

2
00:00:03,770 --> 00:00:05,071
I don't even remember what I just did.

3
00:00:05,071 --> 00:00:06,606
I hope it was okay.

4
00:00:10,043 --> 00:00:11,511
Your Zhou Youzhi...

5
00:00:12,812 --> 00:00:13,880
was really brave.

6
00:00:15,281 --> 00:00:16,516
Well, your Chen Tianyou...

7
00:00:16,516 --> 00:00:17,917
made it easy for him to be.

8
00:00:18,418 --> 00:00:20,754
Still, it's been a long time coming.

9
00:00:21,187 --> 00:00:22,555
Seven whole years.

10
00:00:34,167 --> 00:00:35,101
Thank you.

11
00:00:35,668 --> 00:00:36,903
Congrats on finishing the show.

12
00:00:41,041 --> 00:00:42,542
Don't be like Tianyou, though.

13
00:00:43,042 --> 00:00:44,511
Don't just disappear now that we're done.

14
00:00:52,952 --> 00:00:54,187
I'm so happy!

15
00:01:06,466 --> 00:01:07,367
What's up?

16
00:01:15,475 --> 00:01:16,376
Let's go.

17
00:01:17,477 --> 00:01:19,312
Come on, let's go grab a bite.

18
00:01:21,714 --> 00:01:22,449
Let's go!

19
00:01:38,865 --> 00:01:41,801
I know you wouldn't...

20
00:01:41,801 --> 00:01:45,405
give your all for nothing.

21
00:01:45,405 --> 00:01:48,508
You just want to make up...

22
00:01:48,508 --> 00:01:51,945
for all those past regrets.

23
00:01:51,945 --> 00:01:54,881
Love is what keeps happiness...

24
00:01:54,881 --> 00:01:59,919
from being taken for granted.

25
00:01:59,919 --> 00:02:04,757
The happiness we deserve.

26
00:02:06,326 --> 00:02:08,661
Relax, it's not poisoned.

27
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:11,631
You're always like this when you're busy.

28
00:02:11,631 --> 00:02:13,199
Your stomach hurts, yet you never have meds.

29
00:02:18,938 --> 00:02:20,974
Make up for...

30
00:02:20,974 --> 00:02:23,743
all those past regrets.

31
00:02:24,177 --> 00:02:26,179
Love is what...

32
00:02:26,179 --> 00:02:30,283
keeps happiness from being lost.

33
00:02:31,618 --> 00:02:36,689
The happiness we deserve.

34
00:02:38,224 --> 00:02:39,425
You're such a softie.

35
00:02:39,826 --> 00:02:41,494
Do you carry medicine for everyone in that bag?

36
00:02:42,562 --> 00:02:43,530
Are you kidding?

37
00:02:43,530 --> 00:02:44,764
Why would I look after them?

38
00:02:47,934 --> 00:02:50,303
You're a health nut who never misses a meal.

39
00:02:50,904 --> 00:02:52,438
And your guy is the same way.

40
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:54,541
So why even carry stomach meds?

41
00:02:55,141 --> 00:02:56,509
It's just a habit.

42
00:02:58,478 --> 00:03:00,113
Well, it's a bad one.

43
00:03:00,113 --> 00:03:01,381
You should just toss them.

44
00:03:02,982 --> 00:03:03,950
You two definitely dated.

45
00:03:04,784 --> 00:03:06,186
Oh, shut it.

46
00:03:08,955 --> 00:03:10,056
Alright, listen up.

47
00:03:10,056 --> 00:03:11,891
Let's hear how the tracks sound together.

48
00:03:11,891 --> 00:03:13,726
Your voices go really well together.

49
00:03:13,726 --> 00:03:14,694
They really do.

50
00:03:22,335 --> 00:03:24,504
I gave my "first time" to you.

51
00:03:25,104 --> 00:03:26,072
Same here.

52
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:30,510
But will the fans actually like it?

53
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:31,978
Wait, are you nervous?

54
00:03:31,978 --> 00:03:34,180
I could always make it a solo for you.

55
00:03:35,315 --> 00:03:36,482
Oh, please.

56
00:03:36,482 --> 00:03:38,351
This is our song.

57
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:42,322
Let's take a selfie...

58
00:03:43,223 --> 00:03:44,824
to show the fans.

59
00:03:55,201 --> 00:03:56,469
Look at the camera.

60
00:03:58,004 --> 00:03:58,771
Smile!
